data.description: *** YOU DO NOT NEED FLOOD INSURANCE ***  Welcome to Beacon Square! This beautiful home with 2 Bedrooms, 1 Half of Bathrooms and 1 car garage. Step inside with updated kitchen including granite, new stainless steel appliances, new cabinets, fresh paint inside and outside. Also bathrooms remodeled, the whole house has a laminate floor.  You will enjoy the covered patio in the backyard as you seat outside with the great Florida weather. A full bathroom is inside, and half of bathroom is in the garage. HVAC installed 2021. Roof 10 yrs old. Brand new Water Softner installed.  NO HOA, NO CDD. Easy access to Clearwater or Tampa, less than 2 miles from the Gulf of Mexico to enjoy a fishing trip. Plenty of shopping, restaurants, pharmacy, and beaches. This is an excellent opportunity to own this gorgeous house.   Owner is motivated to sell.
